snippet.textDisplay:
As a proud Egyptian I’m very happy there happens to be a fellow Egyptian contributing to this beautiful song. 🇪🇬🇪🇬🇪🇬🩵♥️
I’ve just come across this and I love everything about it, I love the rhythms and voices of everyone involved, and it’s very beautiful how everyone is singing in harmony regardless of the very diverse backgrounds they come from and the different languages they’re singing in, and most importantly, I love how good music is always there to unify people when everything else in the world fails to do so.
